1. Disconnect the power cables;
2. Remove the battery with a toolbox;
3. Find a charged battery;
4. Install the charged battery.

1. Open the coolant reservoir;
2. Find a new bottle of coolant;
3. Pour it into the coolant reservoir;
4. Close the reservoir.

1. Open the oil reservoir;
2. Find a new bottle of oil;
3. Pour it into the oil reservoir;
4. Close the reservoir.

1. Take out the burnt fuses;
2. Find a new package of fuses;
3. Install the new fuses.

1. Find a scissor jack;
2. Place the scissor jack besides the tire;
3. Remove the flat tire with a toolbox;
4. Find a new tire;
5. Install the new tire.

1. Open the fuel tank;
2. Find a new can of fuel;
3. Pour it into the fuel tank;
4. Close the tank.
